bgm.name: ダンジョン19(静寂に潜む闇)171007_95bpm

parameters:
\n<Ladro>Phew... I've finally made it... It was quite a detour, but
I've managed to get down to the slum residential area. Given
what I've got, they were particularly persistent today...

\n<Ladro>Well, it's a good thing I usually send out a notice
beforehand. ♥ "When you're aiming for a big score, breaking
a promise suddenly thins out the guards," just like mama
said. ♥

\n<Ladro>Such a huge gemstone... kufufu ♥ I can buy anything ♥ I can
eat to my heart's content ♥

\n<\n[1]>In the moonlit night~♪ There's no way~♪ A cat can escape~♪
meow-ow-ow ♥

\n<\n[1]>Today for sure you'll be caught... caught... please let
yourself be caught? Huh? I had my line thought out, but now
I can't remember!

\n<Ladro>...(Well, honestly, this was all expected. \n[1]'s agility
is troublesome.)

\n<Ladro>...(I'll take away their mobility with ice magic... and
then...)

\n<Ladro>(I don't want to hurt them too much... so I guess there's no
choice but to go with that method.)

\n<Ladro>You know, I've already figured out your weakness ♥ After
all, look at last time. Right? ♥ Kusukusu ♥

\n<Ladro>Your face turned so red ♥ It was really cute ♥ I want to see
that face again ♥ Show it to me one more time ♥

\n<\n[1]>Nyaa!! Wh-why are you stripping? St-stop it, it's
embarrassing for me! Don't you have any sense of shame?
\n<\n[1]>Ugh...♥ Do-don't strip! Sh-shame, don't you have any...!

\n<Ladro>Sense of shame? Not at all! I left such things locked away
in a drawer at home. Locked with a key! Ahaha!

\n<Ladro>(It's working, it's working. Calm down, Ladro. I absolutely
cannot be caught here. No matter what it takes.)

\n<Ladro>Fufu ♥ Can you fight? You can't even look at me properly ♥
Kusukusu ♥ If you stay still, big sis will do something nice
for you ♥
\n<Ladro>Don't resist ♥ It's better for both of us that way ♥
